title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 21 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 21 2022
description:
Senator Rand Paul joins Clay and Buck to react to the latest news on Ukraine and the CDC. Harris statements on Ukraine make no sense. Left wing radio host says GOP rooting for covid, Russia, supply-chain issues. Buck annoyed by child blasting Mickey Mouse DVD on flight. Twitter reacts to Clay's take on the Juwan Howard punch. C&B preview tomorrow's show with President Trump . Canadian actress Evangeline Lilly speaks out against Trudeau's trucker hypocrisy.
